{"type": "article", "id": 26018, "title": "玄武岩灯", "description": "", "date": "2016-04-27T07:19:32Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 400262, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 24, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160702115053qlftKeMBUWLx7FbI.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p class=\"medium-insert-images-wide\">比利时设计组合 <a href=\"http://levisarha.com/\" target=\"_blank\">LeviSarha</a> 推出的这款台灯名叫 Drill，由在当地颇为常见的玄武岩所制成。设计师 Levi Dethier 和 Sarha Duquesne 使用岩芯钻将一段圆柱形的部分取出，组装后的造型传递出了一股极简的风格。<br></p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201607021150524U9fNpdBX0qSa86n.gif\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"gif\">\r\n</figure></div>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702115052scNxKi8mW2pnkR7r.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702115052Lq3ktweEcfI9BH6x.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702115053lDQsjkErJOhi0ePH.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><figure class=\"placeholder\"></figure></div>\n\n\n"}